      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "a4cdff44196320cb",
      "text": "Group organisation traditionally requires a coordinated central management group or committee. This is no simple task. Here we explore some of the known and documented issues they face. "
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "34b92d3fe7044940",
      "text": "The following discussion is aimed mainly at political or community organisational forms, but the considerations outlined here also apply to any organisational structure with a traditional central control hierarchy."
