      "text": "# Time"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "29f1441cb680b509",
      "text": "Time is a precious resource at the centre. A few people have to manage the conflicting and shifting demands of a large number of individuals and groups."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "ffa4eda036d294f2",
      "text": "While at the peripheries individuals may have time and energy to offer, the centre suffers the problem that to avail themselves of these resources requires management time, which they simply do not have enough of."
    },
